Package: SurveySolutionsAPI
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive API access to your Survey Solutions Server
Version: 0.6.2
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Wild", email = "mwild@worldbank.org", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This packages implements all the currently available POST, GET, and PATCH
    calls to the Survey Solutions RESTfull API. It contains several convenience functions to
    facilitate these operations, and can handle small impact evaluations as well as large
    scale cenuses.
